    "updated_at": "2015-04-07T02:10:56Z",
    "body": "Thanks for looking into this. The documentation doesn't actually state this, should I submit a PR to fix that. I think it could be clearer.\n\nAlso, that page, which I had read previously talks about using `BrowserWindow` rather than `BrowserWindowProxy` as there are limited features implemented with `BrowserWindowProxy`.\n\nIf I'm waiting to access the full features of `BrowserWindow`, how would I go about achieving this in a context in which `window.opener` exists?\n"
