    "updated_at": "2015-04-07T03:27:59Z",
    "body": "If I wasn't to use `window.open` and `window.opener` but wanted to achieve communication between my primary window and my opened window (while having the full control that BrowserWindow offers), is it best to just use the [IPC module](https://github.com/atom/atom-shell/blob/master/docs/api/ipc-main-process.md) and then route communication between the two windows using a custom function to proxy the messaging?\n"
  },
